{"tid":1460392,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：冀眼部受傷少女早日康復","createTime":"2019-08-13T02:44:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:29:30.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"103d2450f629c95e8747d9138e47aa249ed2e7fd","tid":1460392,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:44:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20190813_20190813-102026.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20190813_20190813-102026.jpg&h=bece744c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥表示，希望在星期日示威中眼部受傷的少女能早日康復，在方便時願意前往探望，又指對示威中受傷的每一人，都感到心痛。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，見到不少評論或圖片，都不是基於已有的證據和事實，認為對於一些未掌握的事實，要讓警方有時間搜證。<br />\n<br />\n對於警方喬裝不同人士拘捕示威者，林鄭月娥說作為行政長官，不會直接指示警方的行動部署，又指警方高層已經解釋是特殊情況下的調查方法，不能認為警方是做了不對的事，因為執法是警隊的使命。<br />\n<br />\n她又回應警方在葵芳站施放催淚彈，指也屬特殊情況，認為在電光火石之間，警員要維護安全，在艱難過程中作決定。"},{"pid":"15401c36fb35f81b6ee5c65fdd6dd1b31731f524","tid":1460392,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:44:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1152345&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1152345%26csid%3D261_341&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y9%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=60d40416\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1152345&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"f6c8d7609386639da5d7329c484d426e4aeff108","tid":1460392,"uid":303556,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:44:52.000Z","msg":"你收皮啦林奠"},{"pid":"9dd6b3911f9fb103281c29146ffe9c5aaf6a9ac7","tid":1460392,"uid":156327,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:48:43.000Z","msg":"準備割席<br />\n禽日鄧炳強啲語氣咁林 都似想割席<br />\n<br />\n前線警犬準備變condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}